# Local-only secrets loaded by miniflare (via @cloudflare/vite-plugin) when you
# run `bun --filter @brika/signaling dev`. Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and
# fill in real values — `.dev.vars` is gitignored.
#
# Production secrets live in Cloudflare's secret store; set them with
# `wrangler secret put <NAME>`.

# HMAC key for browser tickets. Any 32+ random bytes — generate with:
#   openssl rand -hex 32
TICKET_SECRET=""

# Optional: Cloudflare Realtime TURN credentials. Without these the coordinator
# returns STUN-only, which is fine on most local networks but breaks
# symmetric/CGNAT users (mobile/5G) in production-like setups.
#CF_REALTIME_APP_ID=""
#CF_REALTIME_APP_TOKEN=""

# Optional: comma-separated allowed origins for state-changing /v1/* endpoints.
# Localhost is always trusted; unset → defaults to https://hub.brika.dev.
#ALLOWED_ORIGINS=""
